Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}伦敦 2012
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}失踪 你见过她吗 简·麦克吉伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,梅芙 你还好吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Maeve? You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不 亲爱的 我不好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, love. I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我帮你叫医生吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You want me to call a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,医生可帮不上忙\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor can't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你感觉不到吗 翠西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Can't...can't you feel it, Trish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也没感觉到\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I can't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们 快进屋\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Boys... get indoors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快进去 快让他们进去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Get inside! Get 'em inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 他们可没做什么坏事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's up with you? They ain't doing nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在老桉树上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}In the old gum tree
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他是树丛的欢乐欢乐国王\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Merry, merry king of the bush is he
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,笑呀 笑翠鸟笑呀\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Laugh, kookaburra Laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,笑翠鸟你的生活一定好愉快\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}kookaburra Gay your life must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不安全  - 他们在院子里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They're not safe! - They're in the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,它就喜欢这样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's what it likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它就喜欢趁玩耍的时候\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It likes it when they're playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快让他们进屋里 求求你了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Get 'em in! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他是树丛的欢乐欢乐国王\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Merry, merry king of the bush is he
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,笑呀 笑翠鸟笑呀\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Laugh, kookaburra Laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,笑翠鸟你的生活一定好愉快\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}kookaburra Gay your life must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我会好好看着他们的 走吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Right, I've got my beady eyes on 'em. Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  - 汤姆\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No! - Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁  - 他去哪了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What are you? - Where's he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我们的孩子干什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What do you want with our children?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}神秘博士 第二季第十一集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}畏惧她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}肖恩·沃德\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}最热单曲 快下载吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这次是不远的未来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So, near future, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不过一时心血来潮 但这次就卡在了这里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I had a passing fancy. Only it didn't pass. It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,第三十届奥林匹克运动会\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Thirtieth Olympiad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 我怎么没想到 太棒了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No way! Why didn't I think of this? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那些希腊裸男就好像昨天才见过\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Only seems like yesterday a few naked Greek blokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到处扔着铁饼\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}were tossing a discus about,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在沙地上玩摔跤\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}wrestling with each other in the sand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,周围的人群低吼着\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}as the crowds stood around baying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不 等等 那是地中海俱乐部\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, wait a minute, that was Club Med.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,正好赶上今晚的开幕式\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just in time for the opening ceremony tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,觉着你会喜欢 上次伦敦奥运可是轰动一时\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I thought you'd like that. Last one they had in London was dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,温布利 1948\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Wembley, 1948.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢得不得了 又回去重新看了一次\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I loved it so much that I went back and watched it all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,拿火炬的小伙伴\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Fella carrying the torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,非常可爱 他叫干什么来着\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Lovely chap. What was his...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰·马克吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}John, Mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,腿像洗烟斗的 却像灵犬一样强壮\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Legs like pipe-cleaners but strong as a whippet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个年代 所有人都会去茶会  - 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}In those days, everyone had a tea-party to go to. - Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃过上面撒了脆滚珠的蛋糕吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You ever have cakes with crunchy ball-bearings on top?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,博士你应该看看这个  - 要知道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor! You should see this! - You know... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,整个银河系就找不出\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Nobody else in this entire galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个做可食用滚珠的星球 天才\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}has ever bothered to make edible ball-bearings. Genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得是谁拐走了他们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's taking them do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}失踪人口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把孩子们从这样一条普通的街上劫走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Snatching children from a thoroughly ordinary street like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这里这么冷\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And why's it so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么东西给这里降温\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Something's reducing the temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}失踪 你见过他吗 戴尔·希克斯 失踪日期 2012年7月27日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,上面说都是这周失踪的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Says they all went missing this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么有人要这么做\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Why would a person do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你觉得是人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What makes you think it's a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是什么 都让这条街的人吓到死\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Whatever it is, it's got the whole street scared to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor, what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了 今天第五起 这不寻常 是吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There you go! Fifth today! That's not natural, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道怎么回事 离上次保养还不到一个月\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't know what happened. I had it serviced less than a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别解释了 兄弟\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't even try and explain it, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所有车都这样 简直疯了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All the cars are doing it and you know what, it's bonkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,疯了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bonkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 兄弟 我帮你推\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come on, then, pal, I'll help you shift it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你越早上路 就会越开心\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Quicker you're on your way, the happier you'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,走起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要帮忙吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Do you want a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我们可以 亲爱的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, we're all right, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别嘴硬 我比我看上去有力气\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, you're not. I'm tougher than I look, honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事常发生吗  - 谢谢 兄弟\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Does this happen a lot? - Cheers, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经推了一周了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Been doing it all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,自从那些孩子开始失踪 就这样了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Since those children started going missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对 差不多吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yeah. Suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,痒痒\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hmm, tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你玩什么把戏\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我 蛇梯棋\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}My, um... Snakes And Ladders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,壁球也不错 相当不错\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Quite good at squash... Reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我又乱开玩笑了吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm being facetious, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's no call for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所有车都熄火 市政快疯了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Every car cuts out. Council are going nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们费了好些力气 改路名\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They've given this street the works - renamed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我填平所有坑洼路面\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've been Tarmacking every pothole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看看 漂亮吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at that. Beauty, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为奥林匹克火炬\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yep, and this is all because that Olympic torch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,会在最后经过这里 就在那边\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}comes right by the end of this close. Just down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都要完美 对吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Everything's gotta be perfect, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜就是不完美\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Only it ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们玩耍的时候被劫走了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It takes 'em when they're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,被什么带走  - 丹尼 简 戴尔\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What takes them? - Danny, Jane, Dale...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一眨眼就没了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}snatched in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说谎 我是警察\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, I'm not a liar, I'm a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的是 我有警徽和警车\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's what I am. I've got a badge and a police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以证明给你看\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Know what I have to get. I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这附近见够警察了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We've had coppers poking around here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来听起来一点也不像他们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and you don't look or sound like any of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看 这是我同事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}See? Look! I've got a colleague!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫露易丝  - 她比你更不像警察\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Lewis! - She looks less like a copper than you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,见习新人 发型不对\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Training, new recruit. Not that all hair-dressing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备怎么办\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,警察已经挨家挨户问过了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The police have knocked on every door
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没线索 什么都没有\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}no clues, no leads, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们有时候是会离家出走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Kids run off sometimes, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是会  - 我亲眼看见的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's what they do. - I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,戴尔·希克斯在你院子里玩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Dale Hicks in your garden playing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和汤姆一起 然后就\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}with your Tommy and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在我面前噗地一下\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,像他从没去过那里一样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Like he was never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不用跑出这条街找\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's no need to look any further than this street.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手就在我们当中\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's right here amongst us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不如  - 为什么不从他开始\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Why don't we...? - Why don't we start with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这街上来了好些个人 没日没夜\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's been all sorts in this street, day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是为了奥运会修路\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Fixing things up for the Olympics!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可你真够磨蹭的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And taking a long time about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为 我们应该...\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm of the opinion, that all we gonna do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚说的是诽谤  - 我才不管\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look the word you just said. That's slander! - I don't care what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们  - 我要她道歉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I think we need to just... - I want an apology of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别找他的茬  - 对 别找我的茬\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Stop picking on him! - Yeah, stop picking on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别装作没看见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And stop pretending to be blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是魔鬼  - 我才不信鬼\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's evil! - I don't believe in evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你信的是铺路工人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You believe in Tarmackers with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,车里都藏着绑架来的小孩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}stuck loads of kidnapped kiddies in their van!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是这个意思  - 你们别抱团好吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's not what she's saying! - Stop ganging up on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,心虚了 是吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Feeling guilty, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,手都放嘴唇上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Fingers on Lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的六天\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}In the last six days,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这里有三个孩子被偷走了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}three of your children have been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,凭空消失了 对吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Snatched out of thin air, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我能不能\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Er, can I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看看周围\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,直到这事之前 这条街还很安全\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}This was a safe street till it came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是一个人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's not a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不愿意说 那我来说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'll say it if no-one else will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你或许是警察也或许不是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Maybe you're coppers and maybe you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你是什么 能不能帮帮我们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I don't care who you are, can you please help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你要手帕吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You want a hanky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你没闻到吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Can you smell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这味道像什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's it remind you of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,某种 金属\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Sort of...metal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼·爱德华兹骑着自行车进来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Danny Edwards cycled in one end
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,却没从另一头出现\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but never came out the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Whoa, there it goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快看我雄壮多毛的手背上的汗毛\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at the hairs on the back of my manly hairy hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那味道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And there's that smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,烧断的保险丝之类的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A burnt fuse plug or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还有残余能量\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's a residual energy in the spots
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,留在孩子们消失的地方\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}where the kids vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是何物 这么做都消耗了不少能量\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Whatever it was, it used an awful lot of power to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你总要下楼的 克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You have to come down some time, Chloe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我很忙 妈妈\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm busy, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这里 你一定消耗了不少雨林\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at it in here. You must've used up half a rainforest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是戴尔\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你画的他这么悲伤\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Why did you draw him so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我画的他悲伤\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I didn't draw him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,戴尔让自己难过的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Dale made himself sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要给他画一个朋友\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So I'm going to draw him a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他需要的 更多朋友\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's what he needs - more friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你看电视了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Have you seen the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}直播 奥运会倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看 这会让你高兴点 火炬要来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look, this'll cheer you up. The torch is getting close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,会从我们的街上经过\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It'll pass right by our street.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚 他们会在体育场点燃奥运圣火\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Tonight they'll light the Olympic flame in the stadium
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都会关注这个城市\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and the whole world will be looking at our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是觉得自己在经历着什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I mean, doesn't that make you feel part of something? ..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊  - 我正忙呢 妈妈\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe? - I'm busy, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你累了 克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You're tired, Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚又听到你尖叫了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I heard you calling out again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  - 做噩梦了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's fine. - Nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我在画画\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不论你梦到什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Whatever they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那都只是梦 你知道吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}they're just dreams, you do know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没法伤害你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They can't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我很忙 除非你想让我画你 妈妈\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm busy! Unless you want me to draw you...Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你想宅在这 那么好吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If you want to stay cooped up in here, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,随便你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'll leave you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是个漂亮的小朋友\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, aren't you a beautiful boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我试着留背头了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Thanks. I'm experimenting with back-combing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我养过一只和你一样的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I used to have one like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢猫\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm not really a cat person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,当你被修女猫威胁以后\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Once you've been threatened by one in a nun's wimple,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就再也感受不到其中的快乐了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}it kind of takes the joy out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 小猫咪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come here, puss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛去那里面\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What d'you want to go in there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,离子残留 天哪 这需要些技巧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ion residue. Blimey! That takes some doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,从空间时间中取走一个活物\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just to snatch a living organism out of space-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像小孩说"我要这个" 令人赞叹\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}This baby's like, "I'm having some of that!" I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,猫被传送了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So the cat's been transported.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它可以储存相当多的离子能量\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It can harness huge reserves of ionic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要找到能量来源\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We need to find the source of that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,找到来源你就能找到\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Find the source and you will find...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,偷走小孩和毛茸茸小动物的那东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}whatever has taken to stealing children and fluffy animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你能看到什么 盯紧点 露易丝\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}See what you can see. Keep 'em peeled, Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你找了朋友 你却还在难过\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've given you friends and you still moan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,难过 难过 难过 你们很幸运\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Moan, moan, moan. You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都在一起 你们不知道一个人的滋味\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You're all together. You don't know what it is to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们知道 你们会感谢我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If you did, you'd be thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗 小猫咪 你被困住了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Is that you, puss cat? You trapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不要打开 不要打开 不要打开\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Not gonna open it, not gonna open it, not gonna open it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呆着别动\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Okey-dokey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还好 谢谢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yeah. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No probs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我想给你五块钱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'll give you a fiver if you can tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你说出这是什么 我一点也想不出来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}what the hell it is cos I haven't got the foggiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我能说你刚才杀了它\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, I can tell you you've just killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,它本来就不是活的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It was never living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它靠能量活动\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's animated by energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,和抓人时的能量一样 这么不起眼\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The same energy that's snatching people. So dinky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可以到处走的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The go-anywhere creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,能塞进口袋 交朋友\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Fits in the pocket. Makes friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,打动你老板 聚会时缓解尴尬气氛\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Impresses your boss. Breaks the ice at parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hi, ho, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看看\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧  - 上面说什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Get out of here! - What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是石墨\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's graphite!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,基本就是和HB铅笔同样的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Basically the same material as an HB pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我被一团铅笔线攻击了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I was attacked by a pencil scribble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,铅笔线生物\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A scribble creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,从离子能量中获得生命\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}brought into being with ionic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在对付的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Whatever we're dealing with,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可以创造生物 也能夺走生物\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}it can create things as well as take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么要做个线团生物\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But why make a scribble creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可能出错了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Maybe it was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 你涂一团线\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I mean, you scribble over something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在想要涂掉的东西上 像画一样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}when you want to get rid of it, like a drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,像\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小朋友的画\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}child's...drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过它就在街上  - 大概吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You said it was in the street. - Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩  - 对啊 什么女孩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The girl. - Of course! ..What girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她身上有某种东西让我害怕\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Something about her gave me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕她妈妈也怕她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Even her own mum looked scared of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你在推理吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Are you deducting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是的  - 警察的直觉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I think I am. - Copper's hunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,请求追查 警官\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Permission to follow it up, Sarge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我是博士 这是罗丝\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hello, I'm the Doctor and this is Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以见见你女儿吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Can we see your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No! You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 再见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}OK. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么要见克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Why do you want to see Chloe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这条街上发生了很有趣的事情\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, there's some interesting stuff going on in this street
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我想\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I just thought... Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想她可能能够帮我们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}we thought that she might like to give us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思打扰了  - 对 不好意思\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Sorry to bother you. - Yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是继续忙吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We'll let you get on with things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人忙吧 再见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}On your own. Bye again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮她吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Can you help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,火炬接力者正在往商场跑去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'The torch-bearer is running up towards the Mall...'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她大部分时间呆在房间里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She stays in her room most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过和她说话\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I try talking to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但就好像对着个墙壁说话似的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but it's like trying to speak to a brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有回应 只说要一个人呆着\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She gives me nothing, just asks to be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊的父亲呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What about Chloe's dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊的父亲一年前死了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe's dad died a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是认识他就不会这么说了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You wouldn't be if you'd known him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去问个好吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, let's go and say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我先去看看 她可能睡着了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I should check on her first, she might be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么怕她 翠西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Why are you afraid of her, Trish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在你见她之前 我想先告诉你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I want you to know, before you see her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她真的是一个很棒的孩子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}that she's really a great kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信她一定是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm sure she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她在学校从不惹麻烦\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She's never been in trouble at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该看看她去年的报告\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You should see her report from last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都是优和良\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}As and Bs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能用一下洗手间吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Can I use your loo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她参加了合唱团\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She's in the choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她还在敬老院唱歌\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She sings in old folks' homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,任何一位母亲都会为她骄傲 你懂吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Any mum would be proud, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在你见她之前 我想先告诉你这些 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I want you to know these things before you see her, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为现在 她不是她自己\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}because right now, she's not herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是克洛伊·韦伯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm Chloe Webber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗 克洛伊·韦伯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}How are you doing, Chloe Webber?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我很忙 我在做事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm busy. I'm making something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是 妈妈\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Aren't I, Mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过 她很久没睡了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And like I said, she's not been sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你在画画呀\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But you've been drawing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我画得很烂\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,火柴人就是我的极限了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Stick men are about my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我能这样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Can do this though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你行吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们哭个不停  - 克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They don't stop moaning. - Chloe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过帮他们 但他们还是一直哭\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I try to help them but they don't stop moaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在哭  - 我们可以在一起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who don't? - We can be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  - 别碰我 妈妈\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Sweetheart... - Don't touch me, Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我很忙 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm busy... Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊 别扫兴啊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come on, Chloe, don't be a spoil-sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你在忙什么大事呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's the big project?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我可想知道了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm dying to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你在上面做什么呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What are you making up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要来伤害你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm coming to hurt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看这个\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行谢谢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一张画 人的脸  - 什么脸\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A drawing - face of a man. - What face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,最好别  - 你画了些什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Best not. - What have you been drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天画的他  - 谁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I drew him yesterday. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  - 你爸爸\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Dad. - Your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但他已经走很久了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But he's long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊 这个世界那么美好 为什么画他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe, with all the lovely things in the world, why him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我梦到他 盯着我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I dream about him...staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我们已经忘掉他了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I thought we were putting him behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么回事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在一起  - 对\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We need to stay together. - Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是你 我们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, not you, us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在一起 一切都会好的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We need to stay together and then it will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,翠西 那些画\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Trish...the drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过克洛伊的画能做什么么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Have you seen what Chloe's drawings can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谁允许你进她房间的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who gave you permission to come into her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Get out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们说说这些画 克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Tell us about the drawings, Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再听下去了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I don't wanna hear any more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但她爸爸的画像\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But that drawing of her dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到了 他会说话\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I heard a voice, he spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了 这些都是小孩的画 出去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He's dead! And these? They're kids' pictures! Now get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊有能力 我不知道是怎么回事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe has a power and I don't know how,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但她带走了丹尼·爱德华兹 戴尔·希克斯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but she's used it to take Danny Edwards, Dale Hicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她用能力夺走小孩  - 出去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She's using it to snatch the kids! - Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看到画会动吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Have you seen those drawings move?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我什么都没看到  - 不 你见过\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No! I haven't seen anything. - Yes, you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼角瞥见过  - 不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Out of the corner of your eye. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你无视掉了 因为不然你还能怎样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And you dismissed it because what choice you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你见到了无法解释的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You've seen something you can't possibly explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你忽略掉 任何人一提你就会生气\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You dismiss it rite? And if anyone mentions it, you get angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以再也没有人敢说  - 她是个孩子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}so it's never spoken of ever again. - She's a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然而你害怕她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And you're terrified of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但找不到人倾诉 因为谁会相信\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But no one to turn to because who's going to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼角看到的东西呢 没人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the things you see in the corner of your eye? No-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:21:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Except me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来帮你的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那些画 它们是活的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Those pictures, they're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她画人 人就进了画里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She draws people and they end up in her pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,离子能量\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ionic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊收集这种能量 然后偷走孩子们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe's harnessing it to steal those kids
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,放到离子能量笔里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}in placement some kind of holding pen made up of ionic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那衣柜里的地狱爸爸怎么说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And what about the dad from hell in her wardrobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我要说多少次 他死了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}How many times do I have to told you, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就一个死人来说他的声音可够大的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, he's got a very loud voice for a dead bloke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果活物能变成画\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If living things can become drawings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那么画或许也能变成活的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}then maybe drawings can become living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊现实的爸爸已经死了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe's real dad is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可那个噩梦里造访她的爸爸还没有\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But not the one who visits her in her nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个爸爸非常真实\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That dad seems very real,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,既然已经被画出来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and since that she's drawn him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他离闯进这个世界只有一步之遥\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}he's a heartbeat away from crashing into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他在世的时候对她非常不好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She always got the worst of it when he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 一个12岁女孩怎么会做到这一切\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor, how can a 12-year-old girl be doing any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去问问吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不错\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能  - 没问题 相信他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I can't let him... - it's OK. Trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在可以谈谈了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now we can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I want Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别管她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I want Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要克洛伊·韦伯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I want Chloe Webber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我的小姑娘做了什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What have you done to my little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.62,0:23:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 这是什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我在跟你说话\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm speaking to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,利用这个人类孩童的实体\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the entity that is using this human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我要求依照《影子宣言》谈判\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I request parlez in compliance with The Shadow Proclamation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不在乎什么影子什么谈判\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I don't care about shadows or policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那你在乎什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So what do you care about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想交朋友\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I wanna make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.71,0:24:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你很孤独 我知道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You're lonely, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说出你的身份\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Identify yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是众多之一\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I am one of many.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我与兄弟姐妹一起旅行\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I travel with my brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的旅行没有尽头\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We take an endless journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是你寿命的几千倍\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A thousand of your lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.70,0:24:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在只有我一人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But now I am alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌这样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这不公平 我讨厌这样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's not fair. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.82,0:24:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,报上姓名\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Name yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.02,0:24:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,艾索洛斯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Isolus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.60,0:24:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是艾索洛斯 难怪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You're Isolus, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.76,0:24:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们旅行从深域开始\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Our journey began in the Deep Realms
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.94,0:24:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾是一家\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}when we were a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.27,0:24:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.47,0:24:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,艾索洛斯的母亲 在深空漂浮\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The Isolus mother, drifting in deep space.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.37,0:24:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 她抛下成千上万孢子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}See, she jettisons millions of fledgling spores
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.55,0:24:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是她的孩子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}her children.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,艾索洛斯是一种感情充沛的生物\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The Isolus are empathic beings of intense emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.22,0:24:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当他们离开母亲后\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}When they're cast off from their mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.27,0:24:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的情感联结\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}their empathic link,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.35,0:24:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们互相之间的需要让他们活下去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}their need for each other, is what sustains them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.95,0:25:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要在一起 不能分开\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They need to be together. They cannot be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.30,0:25:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的旅行太长\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Our journey is long.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.96,0:25:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,艾索洛斯的孩子们在荚内\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The Isolus children travel, each inside a pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.02,0:25:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,靠着太阳潮汐的热量和能量漂游\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They ride the heat and energy of solar tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.11,0:25:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要成千上万年\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And it takes thousands
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.87,0:25:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,才能长大成年\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and thousands of years for them to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.16,0:25:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,成千上万年在太空漂游\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Thousands of years just floating through space?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.60,0:25:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怜 他们不会无聊到疯吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Poor things. Don't they go mad with boredom?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.19,0:25:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会游戏\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We play.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.18,0:25:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 玩游戏\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You...play?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.17,0:25:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们旅行时 他们会玩游戏\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}While they travel, they play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.24,0:25:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们用离子能量\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They use their ionic power to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.41,0:25:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,去创造虚构世界 在里面游戏\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}literally create make-believe worlds in which to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.98,0:25:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,机上娱乐系统\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}In-flight entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.48,0:25:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让他们愉悦\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It helps keep them happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.23,0:25:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们愉悦时 就能从对方的爱意中汲取养料\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}While they're happy they can feed off each other's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.01,0:25:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没了爱 他们会迷失自己\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Without it, they're lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.56,0:25:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么来地球\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Why did you come to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.23,0:25:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们太近了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We were too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.40,0:25:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你们的太阳的耀斑\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's a solar flare from your sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.89,0:25:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,产生了太阳潮\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Would have made a tidal wave
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.87,0:25:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,让艾索洛斯的荚分散了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}of solar energy that scattered the Isolus pods.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.17,0:25:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我落到了地球\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Only I fell to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.19,0:26:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兄弟姐妹还在上面\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}My brothers and sisters are left up there
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.99,0:26:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我却触碰不到他们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I can not reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.32,0:26:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,多么孤独\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.22,0:26:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你的荚坠落了 它在哪里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Your pod crashed? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我的荚被热量吸引\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}My pod was drawn to heat
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.16,0:26:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我被克洛伊·韦伯吸引\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I was drawn to Chloe Webber.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.80,0:26:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她就像我一样 孤独\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She was like me - alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.71,0:26:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要我 我需要她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She needed me and I her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.69,0:26:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你与她有共鸣\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You empathized with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.79,0:26:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你想和她在一起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You wanted to be with her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.80,0:26:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她和你一样孤独\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}because she was alone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.30,0:26:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要我的家人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I want my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.23,0:26:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这不公平\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.53,0:26:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白 你想要一个家\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I understand, you want to make a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.09,0:26:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能呆在这个孩子体内 这是不对的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But you can't stay in this child, it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.03,0:26:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能为了自己再偷朋友了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You can't steal any more friends for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.43,0:26:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我很孤独\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I am alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.70,0:26:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊 我来伤害你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe, I'm coming to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.27,0:26:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.44,0:26:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,翠西 你怎么安抚她  - 什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Trish! How do you calm her? - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.47,0:26:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她做噩梦时 你怎么做\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}When she has nightmares, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.55,0:26:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.55,0:26:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么  - 我唱歌\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What do you DO? - I sing to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.42,0:26:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始唱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Start singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.00,0:26:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊 我来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.87,0:27:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,笑翠鸟坐在老桉树上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Kookaburra sits in the old gum tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.34,0:27:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.53,0:27:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.51,0:27:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,笑翠鸟你的生活一定好愉快\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Kookaburra Gay your life must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.77,0:27:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,它找上她因为她很孤独\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It came to her because she was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.64,0:27:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛伊 对不起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, Chloe, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.41,0:27:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他发脾气时总是冲着克洛伊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chloe usually got the brunt of his temper,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.47,0:27:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他喝酒以后就会这样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}when he'd had a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.01,0:27:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他撞车那天我还以为我们解脱了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The day he crashed the car, I thought we were free.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.54,0:27:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为都结束了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I thought it was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.76,0:27:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你和她谈过吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Did you talk to her about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.75,0:27:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想谈\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.51,0:27:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但也许这就是克洛伊孤独的原因\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But maybe that's why Chloe feels so alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.97,0:27:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她有那些关于爸爸的噩梦\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Because she has these terrible dreams about her dad
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她却不能跟你说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but she can't talk to you about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.18,0:27:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她和艾索洛斯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Her and the Isolus  - 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.59,0:27:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,两个孤单的孩子需要对方\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}two lonely kids who needed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.88,0:27:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,它也不会放手 是不是 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It won't stop, will it, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.56,0:27:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,它会不断地拽孩子进去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It'll just keep pulling kids in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.31,0:27:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它渴望被爱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's desperate to be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.68,0:28:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它习惯于拥有一个大家庭\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's used to a pretty big family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.68,0:28:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,多大\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}How big?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.94,0:28:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有40亿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Say around four billion?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.90,0:28:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,人们一周前就开始排队\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The queue started a week ago
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.85,0:28:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,都渴望着能进场\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}for those desperate enough to be inside  - 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.24,0:28:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,人数非常多\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}there are lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.48,0:28:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们预计现场会有8万人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We're expecting a capacity crowd of 80,000
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.47,0:28:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,观看这次开幕式\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}for this evening's opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.66,0:28:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I have to say there's been...'
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.07,0:28:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要找到荚\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We need that pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.56,0:28:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,它坠毁了 难道不会已经毁坏了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It crashed. Won't it be destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.18,0:28:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它吸收了那么多热能\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, it's been sucking in all the heat it can.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.79,0:28:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应该能使它保持状态准备发射\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That should keep it fit to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.21,0:28:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就在不远\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.23,0:28:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,它会留下微弱的能量信号让塔迪斯跟踪到\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It should have a weak energy signature the Tardis can trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.68,0:28:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找到荚 就能阻止艾索洛斯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Once we find it, then we can stop the Isolus.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.61,0:28:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她发烧了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She's running a temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.27,0:28:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在没办法详说 克里斯蒂\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}..I can't go into that now, Kirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.38,0:28:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我们找了医生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes, we've got a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.38,0:28:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对 他说他能帮她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}..Yes, he said he can help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.08,0:28:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以扫描与铅笔线生物\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We can scan for the same trace I picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.91,0:28:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,相同的信号\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}from the scribble creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.65,0:28:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要稍微扩大扫描范围\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just need to widen the field a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.81,0:29:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,艾索洛斯还没开口你就知道它很孤独了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You knew the Isolus was lonely before it told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.11,0:29:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.53,0:29:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂一个人长期旅行的感觉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I know what it's like to travel a long way on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.95,0:29:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,给我石磁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Give me the steino-magnetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.40,0:29:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你左手边的那个\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the thing in your left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.11,0:29:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,听上去你站在它那边\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Sounds like you're on its side.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.81,0:29:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我同情它 仅此而已\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I sympathize, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.19,0:29:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,艾索洛斯给这些人带来了很多痛苦\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The Isolus has caused a lot of pain for these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.07,0:29:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是个孩子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.10,0:29:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以它才找上了克洛伊 两个孤独的小孩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's why it went to Chloe. Two lonely mixed-up kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.36,0:29:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来它像发脾气了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Feels to me like a temper tantrum
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.68,0:29:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,只因为得不到想要的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}cos it can't get its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.09,0:29:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它吓坏了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's scared. Come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.08,0:29:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你也曾经是孩子 给我双体点\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}you were a kid once. Binary dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.00,0:29:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我也知道小孩是什么样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes, and I know what kids can be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.20,0:29:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小恶魔\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Right little...terrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.56,0:29:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,口香糖  - 我有堂表亲\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Gum. - Hey, I've got cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.63,0:29:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们的要求不可能全满足\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Kids can't have it all their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.80,0:29:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是家庭的一部分\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's part of being a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.85,0:29:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那试着理解他们怎么样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And what about trying to understand them?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.71,0:29:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的轻松 你又没有小孩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Easy for you to say, you don't have kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.89,0:29:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前当过父亲\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I was a dad... once.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.52,0:29:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.01,0:30:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们做好了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I think we're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.95,0:30:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,恐惧和孤独是两大原因 罗丝\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Fear. Loneliness. They're the big ones, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.58,0:30:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一些可怕的行为根源就是它们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Some terrible acts have been inspired by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.80,0:30:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但同时我们面对的不是想征服或毁灭的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But then we are not dealing with something that wants to conquer or destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.46,0:30:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想要在这个宇宙通行无阻 你需要很多东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's a lot of things you need to get across this universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.89,0:30:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,曲速引擎 虫洞折射镜\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}warp drive, wormhole refractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.62,0:30:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你最需要什么吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Do you know the thing you need most of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.99,0:30:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要一只可以牵起的手\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You need a hand to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.59,0:30:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我只是在指这个\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, look, I'm pointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.93,0:30:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是荚 它真的在这条街\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's the pod! It IS in the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.75,0:30:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都开始慢慢浮现 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Everything's coming up Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.23,0:30:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大概60厘米宽\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's about two inches across.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.22,0:30:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,灰色 像海鸥蛋 很轻\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Dull grey, like a gull's egg. Very light.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.38,0:30:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些荚利用热能在太阳中穿行 对吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So these pods, they travel from sun to sun, using the heat, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.08,0:30:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不全是靠着爱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So it's not all about love and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.09,0:30:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,荚难道不是只需要热能吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doesn't the pod just need heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.11,0:30:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.30,0:30:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.37,0:31:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 我已经拿走她所有的铅笔了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's OK, I've taken all the pencils off her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.20,0:31:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别管我 我想和克洛伊·韦伯在一起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Leave me alone! I want to be with Chloe Webber!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.44,0:31:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱克洛伊·韦伯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I love Chloe Webber.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.94,0:31:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,放他回来  - 不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bring him back now. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.65,0:31:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你在做什么吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't you realise what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.55,0:31:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他是唯一可以帮你的人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He was the only one who could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.81,0:31:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在放他回来  - 别管我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now bring him back! - Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.28,0:31:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱克洛伊·韦伯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I love Chloe Webber!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.35,0:31:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.40,0:31:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.43,0:31:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 如果你听得见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor, if you can hear me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.44,0:31:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把你救出来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm going to get you out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.44,0:31:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找到荚\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'll find the pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.79,0:31:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让她一个人呆着 不管发生什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't leave her alone, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.51,0:31:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,火炬手离奥林匹克体育场越来越近了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The torchbearer is getting closer to the Olympic Stadium,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.87,0:31:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沿着斯特兰德大街\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}heading down The Strand
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.37,0:31:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,直到在\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'before turning east...'
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.54,0:31:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,热能\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.17,0:31:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,它们靠热能穿行\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They travel on heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.09,0:32:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这成果 像婴儿屁股一样圆滑\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at this finish. Smooth as a baby's bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.06,0:32:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不凹也不凸\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Not a bump or a lump.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.31,0:32:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,凯尔 这条街上前几天\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Kel, was there anything in this street
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有什么东西产生巨大热能\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the last few days giving off a lot of heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.93,0:32:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你可以在上面吃晚饭\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I mean, you could eat your dinner off this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太美了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.81,0:32:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你说说为什么所有车都在这里趴窝\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So you tell me why the other one's got a lump in it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.08,0:32:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个坑我明明和其他几个填得一模一样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}when I gave it the same craftsmanship as I did this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.65,0:32:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,当你想出原因\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, when you've worked it out
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.79,0:32:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以写一本关于铺路的大书\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}put it in a big book about Tarmacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.27,0:32:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这之前 想想过去的六天\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But before you do that, think back six days.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.69,0:32:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,六天前\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Six days?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.83,0:32:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次铺这一块的时候  - 什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}When I was laying this the first time round? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.94,0:32:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我第一次填这个坑\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's when I filled in this pothole for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.69,0:32:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,六天前  - 对\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Six days ago. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.65,0:32:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,热 新鲜沥青\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hot, fresh tar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.89,0:32:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,按照市政的秘密配方混合\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Blended to a secret council recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.46,0:32:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没把配方藏在车里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And I don't keep it in the van.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.87,0:32:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是市政车 快出来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hey! That's a council van! Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.30,0:32:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Whoa! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.74,0:32:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚从市政车里拿走了一把市政铁镐\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You've just removed a council axe from a council van.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.52,0:32:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放回去 别别 这是我的车\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Put it back. No, don't. That's my van.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.29,0:32:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,给我铁镐 等等 住手\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Give me the axe. Wait! No! No! You stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.86,0:33:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你从市政车里面拿走了市政铁镐\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You just took a council axe from a council van
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.89,0:33:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你在挖市政路\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and now you're digging up a council road!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.31,0:33:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找政府举报你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm reporting you to the council!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.47,0:33:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,它选择了这条街上最热的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It went for the hottest thing in the street
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.07,0:33:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的沥青\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}your tar!
