Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.99,0:40:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他也许去别的地方了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Maybe he's gone somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.13,0:40:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在谁来牵起他的手\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who's gonna hold his hand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.57,0:40:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这个\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just look at this  - 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.64,0:40:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,奥林匹克体育场发生完全不可思议的一幕\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}utterly incredible scenes at the Olympic Stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.44,0:40:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,8万名运动员和观众\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}80,000 athletes and spectators,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.95,0:40:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们消失了 又回来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}they disappeared, they've come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.57,0:40:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们回来了 他们重新出现了 不可思议\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They returned. They've re-appeared. It's quite incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.54,0:40:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃 这一定是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bob, this was certainly...'
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.13,0:40:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,8万人 博士在哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}80,000 people, so where's the Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.14,0:40:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I need him!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.72,0:40:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 火炬手似乎遇到了些问题\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hang on! The torch-bearer seems to be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.37,0:40:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,早些时候我们看到一束闪电\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We did see a flash of lightning earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.79,0:41:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎击中他了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}that seemed to strike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.72,0:41:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他受伤了 他肯定有些麻烦了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Maybe he's injured. He's definitely in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.51,0:41:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说奥林匹克精神死了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Does this mean that the Olympic dream is dead?'
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.60,0:41:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.81,0:41:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有个神秘人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's a mystery man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.78,0:41:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他拾起圣火 我们不知道他是谁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He's picked up the flame and we've no idea who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.44,0:41:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他举着圣火 对\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He's carrying the flame. Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.73,0:41:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他举着圣火 没人想阻止他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}he's carrying the flame and no-one wants to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.48,0:41:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经不仅仅是火焰了 鲍勃\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's more than a flame now, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.93,0:41:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这不仅仅是热与光\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's more than heat and light  - 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.15,0:41:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是希望 是勇气 是爱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}it's hope and it's courage and it's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.71,0:41:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 加入你的兄弟姐妹\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Go on, join your brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.86,0:41:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定等了很久\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.15,0:42:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要蛋糕吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.79,0:42:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,头等大事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Top banana!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.79,0:42:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我说多少遍都不嫌多 能吃的滚珠\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I can't stress this enough - ball-bearings you can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.06,0:42:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大师之作\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.49,0:42:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我失去你了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I thought I'd lost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.72,0:42:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的 不会在这样的晚上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Nah, not on a night like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.63,0:42:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚是失而复得的夜晚\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}This is a night for lost things being found.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.72,0:42:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  - 现在去哪里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come on. - What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.76,0:42:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去看奥运会 我们就是为了这个来的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I want to go to the Games, it's what we came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.43,0:42:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,给点提示\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Go on, give us a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.84,0:43:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们哪些项目表现不错\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Which events do we do well in?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.90,0:43:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么说吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I will tell you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.81,0:43:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,巴布新几内亚在铅球项目给了所有人一个惊喜\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Papua New Guinea surprise everyone in the shot-put.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.40,0:43:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 你开玩笑的吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Really? You're joking, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.29,0:43:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.14,0:43:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是认真的还是开玩笑  - 等着瞧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Are you serious or are you joking? - Wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.22,0:43:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道么 他们总是想分开我们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You know what? They keep on trying to split us up,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.25,0:43:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们永远不会得逞\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but they never ever will.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.23,0:43:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,永远别说永远\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Never say "Never ever".
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.80,0:43:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的 我们总是会顺利的 你和我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Nah, we'll always be OK, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.27,0:43:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't you reckon, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.68,0:43:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,空气里有些东西 正在靠近  - 什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Something in the air. Something coming. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.84,0:43:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雨要来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A storm's approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.06,0:45:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(193,145)}在2009年和2014年所做的两次官方民调中\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}本集都是新版最不受喜爱的一集\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}本集剧情启发了部分粉丝 他们发起请愿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}要求DT参加2012伦敦奥运的火炬接力\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}不过最后是十一任博士MS在威尔士参加了火炬接力
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.16,0:43:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个地球大战的故事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}This is the story of war on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.04,0:43:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的孩子很快就会死在战争中\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The valiant child who will die in battle so very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.49,0:43:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它说我会死在战争中  - 那就是它说谎了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Said I was going to die in battle. - Then it lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.75,0:44:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到火炬木\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Welcome to Torchwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.09,0:44:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我早上起来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I woke up one morning and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.04,0:44:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那了 到处都是鬼魂\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}there they all were, ghosts everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.04,0:44:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我是敌人 我现在难道是战俘\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But if I'm the enemy, does that mean I'm a prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.19,0:44:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.79,0:44:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把这个抬去哪里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oi, where are you taking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.86,0:44:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,外星的就是我们的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If it's alien, it's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.40,0:44:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里有个问题 依芙\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We've got a problem down here. Yvonne,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.53,0:44:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听得到吗  - 我们把它送回地狱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}can you hear me? - Send that thing back into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.23,0:44:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.84,0:44:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们面前作威作福\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}lording it over us,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.03,0:44:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,总是认为外星权威高于人类人权\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}assuming alien authority over the rights of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.21,0:44:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是裂缝中渗出的血液\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They're bleeding through the fault lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.50,0:44:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,从他们的世界穿过虚无来到你们的世界\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}walking from their world across the void and into yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.33,0:44:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你没法阻止我们 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You can't stop us, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.80,0:44:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界撞上了另外一个  - 就位\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}This world is colliding with another. - Positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.39,0:44:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.85,0:44:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,赛博人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Cybermen!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.28,0:44:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是一切终结的时刻\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's when it all ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.22,0:44:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我讲述的最后一个故事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}This is the last story I'll ever tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.41,0:44:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}下集预告
